  "date": "2009-07-11 10:00:00",
  "desc": "The Celtic Knot",
  "content": "<p>The Celtic Knot was a great change of pace for us.  The crowd was all there for dinner, which let us play more slower numbers to start the night.</p>

<p>What\'s great was the crowd went with us the whole night.  We sped up the bluegrass tempo as the night continued - and people began to get up and dance</p>

<p>This was also the first time we got to play with Joel in a few shows.  Always a great time when we get to do his songs as they\'re supposed to sound.</p>",
